welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Alderwood Manor, a charming city known for its beautiful parks and friendly community. We hope you have a wonderful stay and take some time to explore all the city has to offer."

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Kenmore Air Harbor SPB Airport, serving both arriving and departing passengers.

terminals.name: Water Terminal
terminals.description: The water terminal at Kenmore Air Harbor SPB Airport, providing access to seaplane flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Boeing Field/King County International Airport serves all commercial and private flights.

terminals.name: South Terminal
terminals.description: The South Terminal at Boeing Field/King County International Airport is primarily used for cargo and general aviation operations.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Renton Airport offers a variety of amenities for travelers including shops, restaurants, and rental car services.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Renton Airport is reserved for private and corporate flights, offering a more exclusive and personalized experience for passengers.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport for all passengers.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Seattle-Tacoma International Airport serves both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: North Satellite Terminal
terminals.description: The North Satellite Terminal at Seattle-Tacoma International Airport primarily serves Alaska Airlines and its affiliates.

terminals.name: South Satellite Terminal
terminals.description: The South Satellite Terminal at Seattle-Tacoma International Airport serves international flights and some domestic flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.
